                <note rend="inline" type="source">125.9532: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the
                        Consul at Tsingtao</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Hawthorne</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1949-07-01T19:00:00-04:00"
                            >July 1, 1949—7 p. m.</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>177. Dept assumes you have protested to local Aliens Affairs Office (urtel 302,
                    June 30). Shld attempt obtain receipt for such removals signed by officer
                    removing.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Acheson</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
